      "title": "Registrar General\u2019s Dept, post offices to provide limited services",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Registrar General\u2019s Department says the issuance of birth, marriage and death certificates through its divisional secretariats and land registry services will be limited to two days per week.",
        "In a media notice, the department said the aforementioned services are provided only on Mondays and Wednesdays during the next 10 days.",
        "Meanwhile, the Post Master General announced that all post offices and sub-post offices across the island will function only on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays in view of the ongoing situation."
      ],
